{"tid":990958,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打擊謠言 WhatsApp限制同一訊息最多轉發5次","createTime":"2019-01-22T04:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T02:12:22.000Z","uid":57677,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9a3c4049bafb872a8d03f69cd8f98867c03908c8","tid":990958,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T04:23:25.000Z","msg":"為打擊錯誤資訊和謠言廣傳，WhatsApp周一（21日）表示，由當日起將會限制全球的WhatsApp用戶轉發短訊次數，每個短訊最多只能轉發5次。WhatsApp將在同日開始更新程式，預料Android用戶將會首先收到更新通知，iOS的用戶將緊隨其後。<br />\n<br />\n公司的政策及通信部副總裁格朗（Victoria Grand）當日宣布此消息。WhatsApp用戶此前可向20個群組或個人轉發短訊，不過隨着印度有WhatsApp用戶去年轉發有人綁架孩童的虛假消息，導致該國有民眾遭其他人執行私刑殺死後，WhatsApp遂於去年7月在印度實施有關措施。<br />\n<br />\n目前WhatsApp在全球擁有15億用戶，公司一直想辦法阻止用戶濫發錯誤資訊和謠言。外界一度憂慮，用戶能夠透過WhatsApp傳播假新聞、假圖片等惡作劇，而無法追尋真正來源。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190121/bkn-20190121191945223-0121_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190121%2Fbkn-20190121191945223-0121_00822_001.html&d=v7jNhCDNvRQ0Kgdfj4AgnDM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=2654d69c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190121/bkn-20190121191945223-0121_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a45ee45ba433b8da944181f406fd1a597285c7d6","tid":990958,"uid":13160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T04:23:55.000Z","msg":"已轉發"},{"pid":"3a429e90143e425a2204e49c62ff53ea2a58f66a","tid":990958,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T04:25:16.000Z","msg":"你知道嗎"},{"pid":"5fe92847447fe16a893e1d7b45675a80c075f69d","tid":990958,"uid":5686,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T04:25:27.000Z","msg":"Copy &gt; Paste &gt; Send 呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65add0f15770be9f839c92ac393c10ea217c703","tid":990958,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T04:25:51.000Z","msg":"地球人是需要管的!"},{"pid":"020a75fc77973acc7a2344a33c0407c351